0.03146226,0.0614299,0.01047864,-0.00577886,-0.02468222,-0.02118394,0.05940901,0.00019706,-0.0359021,0.03168144,0.00036021,0.00431903,-0.07443386,-0.06593472,0.01573854,-0.03440792,0.00128824,-0.06348877,0.13405396,-0.0142506,-0.01618941,-0.03889756,-0.01491738,0.00113409,0.06068959,-0.01021072,0.01750602,0.10761812,-0.00367751,-0.00712031,0.01947601,-0.02706342,0.0191695,0.03488009,0.00510371,0.0092422,-0.00216385,0.04402689,-0.02907315,-0.03303995,-0.12783706,-0.1557456,-0.08868746,0.0343308,-0.04760997,0.02931159,-0.02275526,0.04925763,-0.00350877,0.09028213,0.09408484,0.07072704,0.04014159,-0.04426181,0.02756497,0.00443105,0.00970772,-0.00099362,-0.01321518,-0.00227065,-0.01603256,-0.00023865,0.05095159,-0.00237587,-0.0138003,-0.00343981,-0.03442306,0.1160205,-0.04111053,0.00592368,0.03120084,0.04354046,0.00868719,0.02993299,0.05287381,0.01619974,0.01637779,-0.05242867,-0.02878577,-0.01721326,-0.07362647,0.02803033,0.0529716,-0.01136277,-0.03087258,-0.07284196,-0.0213691,-0.04768335,-0.03879573,-0.06753167,0.05732014,-0.01488683,0.00733349,0.0520994,-0.00195803,0.02247556,-0.02840608,-0.04016332,-0.02184151,-0.04165071,0.01549282,-0.02003475,-0.03863756,0.02063193,-0.04684175,-0.02915614,0.00753733,-0.01158651,-0.0555305,-0.01572702,-0.00009541,0.00946456,0.10710546,0.04837645,-0.0012047,0.04349447,-0.02411266,0.01390528,0.04868967,0.00736729,-0.00455179,0.06807367,0.00123393,0.01292216,0.01902308,0.02807929,-0.0089792,0.03234911,-0.01277715,0.01752558,-0.02161272,-0.06416973,0.02534735,0.00237395,0.00022208,-0.02246465,-0.00298577,-0.3192578,0.04862104,0.00305466,0.00682612,-0.02691148,0.02115961,0.05042987,-0.02656097,-0.12937856,0.02526186,-0.06355071,0.05605391,0.07733507,-0.03541148,0.04004665,-0.06711422,0.05729955,-0.05947156,0.03410547,0.00722463,0.04491334,0.02843405,0.17923735,0.03626667,0.0576618,-0.0288412,0.02672792,0.0500551,0.06504279,-0.00241329,-0.0114717,0.00153399,0.13046378,-0.05809403,0.03089651,0.05525526,-0.05649234,0.03530233,-0.0024617,0.00162524,-0.01149038,0.00190891,-0.10412022,0.06256489,0.11354261,0.03228129,-0.00351833,-0.034364,0.00893448,0.01489554,-0.01619652,0.07197381,0.05660689,0.03647624,-0.01390387,0.06781279,-0.05247262,-0.04369362,-0.03018513,-0.07248013,0.01960877,-0.02390272,0.00908432,0.04264608,0.0263549],"last_embed":{"hash":"1m8plhq","tokens":490}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1m8plhq","at":1769671132888},"key":"01-数学教学/试卷/功底考/FY25功底考-解析版1-10_121-160 1.md#【答案】 0.28","lines":[6,1084],"size":44351,"outlinks":[{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\n\n## 【解析】\n\n设直线 $N O 、 M O$ 的斜率分别为 $k_{1} 、 k_{2}$, 其中 $k_{1}>0, k_{2}<0$,\n\n联立 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{c}y=k_{1} x \\\\ x^{2}+4 y^{2}=4\\end{array}\\right.$ 可得 $\\left(4 k_{1}^{2}+1\\right) x^{2}=4$ ，解得 $x= \\pm \\frac{2}{\\sqrt{4 k_{1}^{2}+1}}$ ，\n\n点 $A$ 在第三象限，则 $x_{A}=-\\frac{2}{\\sqrt{4 k_{1}^{2}+1}}$,\n\n点 $B$ 在第四象限，同理可得 $x_{B}=\\frac{2}{\\sqrt{4 k_{2}^{2}+1}} ，$\n\n且 $k_{1} k_{2}=\\frac{y_{1} y_{2}}{x_{1} x_{2}}=\\frac{x_{1} x_{2}}{16}=-\\frac{1}{4} \\quad \\frac{S_{\\triangle O M N}}{S_{\\triangle O A B}}=\\frac{|O M| \\cdot|O N|}{|O B| \\cdot|O A|}=\\frac{\\left|x_{1}\\right| \\cdot\\left|x_{2}\\right|}{\\left|x_{B}\\right| \\cdot\\left|x_{A}\\right|}=\\frac{\\left|x_{1} \\cdot x_{2}\\right|}{\\frac{2}{\\sqrt{4 k_{1}^{2}+1}} \\cdot \\frac{2}{\\sqrt{4 k_{2}^{2}+1}}}$\n$=\\sqrt{\\left(4 k_{1}^{2}+1\\right)\\left(4 k_{2}^{2}+1\\right)}=\\sqrt{4 k_{1}^{2}+\\frac{1}{4 k_{1}^{2}}+2} \\geq \\sqrt{2 \\sqrt{4 k_{1}^{2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{4 k_{1}^{2}}}+2}=2$,\n当且仅当 $k_{1}=\\frac{1}{2}$ 时，等号成立。\n$\\frac{S_{\\triangle O M N}}{S_{\\triangle O A B}}$ 的取值范围为 $[2,+\\infty)$.\n21. 已知定义在 $(0,+\\infty)$ 上的函数 $y=f(x)$ 的表达式为 $f(x)=\\sin x-x \\cos x$ ，其所有的零点按从小到大的顺序组成数列 $\\left\\{x_{n}\\right\\} \\quad(n \\geq 1, n \\in N)$ 。\n(1) 求函数 $y=f(x)$ 在区间 $(0, \\pi)$ 上的值域;\n\n## 【答案】 $(0, \\pi)$\n\n## 【解析】\n\n由 $f^{\\prime}(x)=\\cos x-(\\cos x-x \\sin x)=x \\sin x$ ，\n\n当 $x \\in(0, \\pi)$ 时, $f^{\\prime}(x)>0$, 即函数 $y=f(x)$ 在区间 $(0, \\pi)$ 上是严格增函数,\n\n且 $f(0)=0, f(\\pi)=\\pi$ ，\n\n所以 $f(x)$ 在区间 $(0, \\pi)$ 上的值域为 $(0, \\pi)$.\n(2) 求证: 函数 $y=f(x)$ 在区间 $(n \\pi,(n+1) \\pi) \\quad(n \\geq 1, n \\in N)$ 上有且仅有一个零点;\n\n## 【答案】证明见解析\n\n## 【解析】\n\n当 $x \\in(n \\pi,(n+1) \\pi)$ 时,\n(1) 当 $n$ 是偶数时， $f^{\\prime}(x)>0$ ，\n\n函数 $y=f(x)$ 在区间 $(n \\pi,(n+1) \\pi)$ 上是严格增函数;\n(2)当 $n$ 是奇数时, $f^{\\prime}(x)<0$,\n\n函数 $y=f(x)$ 在区间 $(n \\pi,(n+1) \\pi)$ 上是严格减函数;\n\n且 $f(n \\pi)=(-1)^{n-1} n \\pi$, 故 $f(n \\pi) \\cdot f((n+1) \\pi)=-n(n+1) \\pi^{2}<0$,\n所以由零点存在定理可知，\n\n函数 $y=f(x)$ 在区间 $(n \\pi,(n+1) \\pi)$ 上有且仅有一个零点.\n(3) 求证: $\\pi<x_{n+1}-x_{n}<\\frac{(n+1) \\pi}{n}$.\n\n## 【答案】证明见解析\n\n## 【解析】\n\n由（2）可知函数 $f(x)$ 在 $(n \\pi,(n+1) \\pi)$ 上有且仅有一个零点 $x_{n}$,\n\n且满足 $f\\left(x_{n}\\right)=\\sin x_{n}-x_{n} \\cos x_{n}=0$, 即 $\\tan x_{n}=x_{n}$ （几何意义: $x_{n}$ 是 $y=\\tan x$ 与 $y=x$ 交点的横坐标）又因为 $f\\left(n \\pi+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\right)=(-1)^{n}$, 故 $f(n \\pi) \\cdot f\\left(n \\pi+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\right)=-n \\pi<0$,\n\n所以由零点存在性定理可知，\n\n函数 $y=f(x)$ 在 $\\left(n \\pi, n \\pi+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\right)$ 上有且仅有一个零点 $x_{n}$,\n\n于是 $x_{n}+\\pi, x_{n+1} \\in\\left((n+1) \\pi,(n+1) \\pi+\\frac{\\pi}{2}\\right), x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right) \\in\\left(-\\frac{\\pi}{2}, \\frac{\\pi}{2}\\right)$\n$\\tan \\left(x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)\\right)=\\tan \\left(x_{n+1}-x_{n}\\right)=\\frac{\\tan x_{n+1}-\\tan x_{n}}{1+\\tan x_{n+1} \\cdot \\tan x_{n}}=\\frac{x_{n+1}-x_{n}}{1+x_{n+1} \\cdot x_{n}} \\quad$ (1)因为 $x_{n+1}-x_{n}>0$, 得\n$\\tan \\left(x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)\\right)>0$ 所以 $x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)>0$, 即 $\\pi<x_{n+1}-x_{n}$;\n（或者 $\\tan x_{n+1}-\\tan \\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)=\\tan x_{n+1}-\\tan x_{n}=x_{n+1}-x_{n}>0$\n$\\left.\\Rightarrow \\tan x_{n+1}>\\tan \\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right) \\Rightarrow x_{n+1}-x_{n}>\\pi\\right)$\n(2) 因为 $\\tan \\left(x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)\\right)=\\frac{x_{n+1}-x_{n}}{1+x_{n+1} \\cdot x_{n}}<\\frac{\\frac{3}{2} \\pi}{x_{n}^{2}}<\\frac{\\frac{3}{2} \\pi}{n^{2} \\pi^{2}}=\\frac{3}{2 n^{2} \\pi}<\\frac{\\pi}{n} \\quad$ 由 (1) 可知, 当 $x \\in\\left(0, \\frac{\\pi}{2}\\right)$\n\n时, 有 $x<\\tan x$ 故 $x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)<\\tan \\left(x_{n+1}-\\left(x_{n}+\\pi\\right)\\right)<\\frac{\\pi}{n}$, 所以 $x_{n+1}-x_{n}<\\pi+\\frac{\\pi}{n}$;\n\n由(1)(2)可知 $\\pi<x_{n+1}-x_{n}<\\frac{(n+1) \\pi}{n}$.\n\n## 上海市松汇区 2024 届高三下学期模拟考质量监控（二模）数学试卷\n\n一、填空题\n\n1. 函数 $y=\\lg (x-2)$ 的定义域为 $\\qquad$\n\n【答案】 $(2,+\\infty)$\n\n【解析】要使函数 $y=\\lg (x-2)$ 有意义,\n\n则 $x-2>0 \\Rightarrow x>2$,\n\n所以函数 $y=\\lg (x-2)$ 的定义域为 $(2,+\\infty)$ ，\n\n故答案为 $(2,+\\infty)$ 。\n2. 在复平面内, 复数 $z$ 对应的点的坐标是 $(1,2)$, 则 $i \\cdot z=$ $\\qquad$ .\n\n【答案】 $-2+i$\n\n## 【解析】\n\n根据复数的乘法运算求解即可.\n由题意知， $z=1+2 i ，$\n\n则 $i \\cdot z=i \\cdot(1+2 i)=-2+i$,\n\n故答案为: $-2+i$\n3. 已知随机变量 $X$ 服从正态分布 $N\\left(3, \\sigma^{2}\\right)$, 且 $P(3 \\leq X \\leq 5)=0.3$, 则 $P(X 5)=$ $\\qquad$ .\n\n【答案】 0.2\n\n## 【解析】\n\n根据题意，结合正态分布的对称性，即可求解。\n因为随机变量 $X$ 服从正态分布 $N\\left(3, \\sigma^{2}\\right)$, 且 $P(3 \\leq X \\leq 5)=0.3$,\n可得 $P(X 5)=0.5-P(3 \\leq X \\leq 5)=0.5-0.3=0.2$.\n\n故答案为: 0.2 .\n4. 已知点 $A$ 的坐标为 $\\left(\\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right)$, 将 $O A$ 绕坐标原点 $O$ 逆时针旋转 $\\frac{\\pi}{2}$ 至 $O P$, 则点 $P$ 的坐标为 $\\qquad$ .\n\n【答案】 $\\left(-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}, \\frac{1}{2}\\right)$\n\n## 【解析】\n\n由题意可求 $\\angle x O A=\\frac{\\pi}{3}, \\angle x O P=\\frac{\\pi}{3}+\\frac{\\pi}{2}=\\frac{5 \\pi}{6}$, 利用任意角的三角函数的定义即可求解.\n因为点 $A$ 的坐标为 $\\left(\\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\right)$, 可得 $\\angle x O A=\\frac{\\pi}{3}$,\n所以 $\\angle x O P=\\frac{\\pi}{3}+\\frac{\\pi}{2}=\\frac{5 \\pi}{6}$,\n可得 $X_{P}=\\cos \\frac{5 \\pi}{6}=-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}, y_{P}=\\sin \\frac{5 \\pi}{6}=\\frac{1}{2}$ ，\n\n所以点 $P$ 的坐标为 $\\left(-\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}, \\frac{1}{2}\\right)$,\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_18_5c993f8d3c7192c2df13g-40.jpg?height=389&width=490&top_left_y=1550&top_left_x=1234","line":947}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"1m8plhq","at":1769671132888}},
